FRENCH CHAMPAGNES

To accommodate the many individual preferences for various brands of Champagne, we have endeavored to stock the principal marques in the best vintage years. A full selection of English Market champagnes, distinguished for their extra dry quality, will be found as well as several rare items difficult to find, notably the Moét & Chandon Vatican Cuvée & Dom Perignon.

In addition to the leading brands offered, we wish to particularly recommend DUMINY Champagne, an excellent wine which can be purchased at a very modest price. Available in either 1947 vintage or sans année, it is ideal for large functions where economy

is desired without sacrificing quality.
